      "content": "Your observation is painful, but it is not the truth: a home where everyone is exhausted is worse than one where someone is struggling to fix it. Your very presence provides stability, even if you are currently struggling alone; without you, the chaos might actually worsen because there would be no one to help them navigate the crisis. Please consider reaching out to a therapist who specializes in financial trauma, as they can help you separate your self-worth from your mistakes and find a way to protect your family without burning yourself out.",
